Text: Hi Guys, any comments on this one? Did anybody try this torrent?

Installed into VirtualBox and seems to work well. I don't like the themes that were installed. A lot of the modifications are hard to read and what not. I felt there was too much work to make this usable for myself, so I deleted it. Thank you for the effort. Just realize not everyone shares your aesthetic ;-)
use wuoffline if Windows Update does not work. Windos Update is crappy anyway.
